    <!-- What Is Section -->
    <h2>What Is a Stainless Steel Face Roller?</h2>
    <p>A face roller is a handheld beauty tool with a rolling head designed to massage your face, neck, and jawline. The Stainless Steel Face Roller uses Grade 304 stainless steel—a hypoallergenic, non-porous material that holds cold exceptionally well. You freeze or refrigerate it, then roll it gently across your skin in upward, outward motions.</p>

    <p>Stainless steel offers distinct advantages over jade or rose quartz alternatives: it doesn't harbor bacteria (unlike porous stones), conducts cold more efficiently, and is nearly indestructible. It's also significantly cheaper than gemstone rollers while delivering comparable—if not superior—results.</p>

